<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="hero" id="skills-hero">
    <div class="skills-wrap">
        <div class="hero-title">
            <h2 class="">My Skills</h2>
            <div class="hero-line"></div>
            <p class="lead">Here are some of the skills I've developed while working on various projects.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 skills-inner">
                <div class="skills-content">
                    <div class="circle-icon">
                        <img class="skills-circle" src="imgs/code_icon.png">
                        <h5>Web Development</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p>Javascript, HTML, and Node.js are my main tools for getting websites up and running. I also have
                        experience with MongoDB and different methods of deployment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 skills-inner">
                <div class="skills-content">
                    <div class="circle-icon">
                        <img class="skills-circle" src="imgs/java_icon.png">
                        <h5>Java</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p>The main language studied at university - I have developed several small apps over the years,
                        using both older API's and newer ones.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-4 skills-inner">
                <div class="skills-content">
                    <div class="circle-icon">
                        <img class="skills-circle" src="imgs/design_icon.png">
                        <h5>Graphic Design</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p>My preferred tools for web design are CSS and Bootstrap. I am familiar with Photoshop for
                        designing and editing as well, slightly less so with Illustrator.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

